    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;necromancy&nbsp;[death, fear, mind-affecting, sonic];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;sorcerer/wizard 6, spiritualist 6, witch 6;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;30 feet<br>\n    <strong>Area</strong>&nbsp;cone-shaped burst<br>\n    \n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;instantaneous and 1 round/level (see text)<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Reflex half and Will negates (see text);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;yes<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You create a cone of spectral energy resembling screaming elven ghosts that deals 1d4 points of damage per caster level (maximum 15d4); a successful Reflex save halves this damage. Any creature that fails its Reflex save must succeed at a Will save or become panicked for 1 round/level.</p>\n</div>\n",
